## 🔴 PROBLEM 4 — SECTION ROWS ARE TOO TALL / BLOATED

**What's wrong:** Each section row is `py-3.5` (14px top + 14px bottom) plus the icon `w-10 h-10`. With 13 sections, users can't see all sections without scrolling. The rows feel heavy and padded.

**Fix:** Reduce padding and icon size:

```tsx
// Change the section button className:
// Before:
className={`w-full text-left group flex items-center gap-4 px-5 py-3.5 hover:bg-zinc-800/40 ...`}

// After:
className={`w-full text-left group flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2.5 hover:bg-zinc-800/40 ...`}
```

Also reduce the gap between icon and text from `gap-4` to `gap-3`, and reduce horizontal padding from `px-5` to `px-4`.

